<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-29-0211 </DOCNO><TEXT>Traveling fish screens experience wear and failures due to continuousor frequent operation that is required for enhanced fish survival. EPRI,under Project RP 1689-9, sponsored the evaluation and monitoring of screensat 16 power plants, in order to develop recommended practices for reliabledesigns. The improvements include motors and controls, and more durableand corrosion-resistant materials, and proper maintenance.</TEXT></DOC>